br.com.global5.loginG5.infra

Class Crud<T extends BaseEntity>

  • java.lang.Object
    • br.com.global5.loginG5.infra.Crud<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Crud<T extends BaseEntity>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Author:
    j r zielinski Helper class to crud an entity Make sure you have a transaction before calling Insert/update or remove. I did not make it transactional to be compatible with JavaEE6 Also cannot be an EJB itself cause EJBs may be shared between clients and entityClass may be lost.
